John Orchard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Orchard 0 John Orchard (15 November 1928 – 3 November 1995) was an English actor. He is probably best remembered for playing Australian anesthesiologist "Ugly John" Black in the first season of M*A*S*H. John_Orchard ( 15_November_1928 – 3_November_1995 ) was an_English_actor .
